Package utils

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Configuration
    Reads content of configuration file and provide the configuration data for the other components.
    Help  
    RuntimeFields
    This class holds fields that are important for more than one Classes and Objects of VeniceHub.
    TTE
    Holds a data item with value, sensor name, data type and timestamp and provides methods for calculating and comparing delays.
    TTEBuffer
    A buffer for TTE objects with random access, to enable fast seeking in log files.
    TTEBufferedReader
    Doing the real work for the DiskReader, reads data from file, parses it into TTE items and caches them, until DiskReader will take them.
    TTEQueue
    A singleton queue that stores data read by VeniceReader objects and provide it for VeniceWriter objects, with delaying items by use of the timestamp.
